===Etymology===
Probably from {{der|en|grc|ἱστός||mast}} + {{m|grc|-γραμμα}}, although it is sometimes claimed to have been derived from {{m|en|historical}} + {{m|en|diagram}}; coined in 1891 by English mathematician {{w|Karl Pearson}}.

